com.kenzan.msl.common.dto

Class AbstractArtistDto

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.kenzan.msl.common.dto.AbstractDto
      • com.kenzan.msl.common.dto.AbstractArtistDto

  • public abstract class AbstractArtistDto
extends AbstractDto
    Common super class for all Artist DTOs. NOTE: It would be nice to define here the columns that all Artist DTOs have in common. Unfortunately the Datastax Mapper does not reflect on super classes when mapping result rows to DTOs.
